com.clover.sdk.v3.inventory

Interface InventoryContract.ItemGroupsAndItemsColumns

  • All Superinterfaces:
    InventoryContract.ItemColumns
    Enclosing class:
    InventoryContract

    public static interface InventoryContract.ItemGroupsAndItemsColumns
extends InventoryContract.ItemColumns
    These column names are used to access fields of ItemGroup which have names identical to Item or which are computed when querying via the ItemGroup#CONTENT_URI_AND_ITEMS URI.
